distanceMax.title: Distance Max
distanceMax.description: Setting this to 0 gives an infinite distance limit

inertiaFactor.title: Inertia Factor
inertiaFactor.description: Higher value results in more inertia. 0 means no inertia.

targetEntity.title: Target Entity
targetEntity.description: Invisible entity to use as the orbit center

moveStartEvent.title: Move Start Event
moveStartEvent.description: Event to fire when camera starts moving

moveEndEvent.title: Move End Event
moveEndEvent.description: Event to fire when camera stops moving

orbitSensitivity.title: Orbit Sensitivity
orbitSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves around the orbit. Higher is faster.

distanceSensitivity.title: Distance Sensitivity
distanceSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves in and out. Higher is faster.

panningSensitivity.title: Panning Sensitivity
panningSensitivity.description: How fast the camera pans. Higher is faster.

orbitSensitivity.title: Orbit Sensitivity
orbitSensitivity.description: How fast the camera moves around the orbit. Higher is faster.

distanceSensitivity.title: Distance Sensitivity
distanceSensitivity.description: How fast the camera zooms in and out. Higher is faster.

panningSensitivity.title: Panning Sensitivity
panningSensitivity.description: How fast the camera pans. Higher is faster.

initialPitchAngle.title: Initial Pitch Angle
initialPitchAngle.description: The fixed angle (in degrees) the camera looks down at.

enableFieldOfViewZoom.title: Enable Field of View Zoom
enableFieldOfViewZoom.description: If true, scroll wheel changes the camera's field of view instead of altitude.

moveSpeed.title: Base Move Speed
moveSpeed.description: Base speed at which the camera moves when panning.

rotateSpeed.title: Base Rotate Speed
rotateSpeed.description: Base speed at which the camera rotates when dragging with the middle mouse button.

zoomSpeed.title: Zoom Speed
zoomSpeed.description: Speed at which the camera zooms in/out or changes altitude with the scroll wheel.

minAltitude.title: Min Altitude
minAltitude.description: Minimum altitude the camera can reach.

maxAltitude.title: Max Altitude
maxAltitude.description: Maximum altitude the camera can reach.

minFieldOfView.title: Min Field of View
minFieldOfView.description: Minimum field of view angle, in degrees.

maxFieldOfView.title: Max Field of View
maxFieldOfView.description: Maximum field of view angle, in degrees.

positionInertia.title: Position Inertia
positionInertia.description: Smoothness of camera position movement. Lower values are smoother.

rotationInertia.title: Rotation Inertia
rotationInertia.description: Smoothness of camera rotation. Lower values are smoother.

invertPanY.title: Invert Forward/Backward Pan
invertPanY.description: Invert the direction of forward/backward panning.

forwardRatio.title: Forward Movement Ratio
forwardRatio.description: Ratio of forward movement when changing altitude (0-1)

verticalRatio.title: Vertical Movement Ratio
verticalRatio.description: Ratio of vertical movement when changing altitude (0-1)

activationKey.description: Key to activate the camera switch
